{
  "stem": "14867.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they instilled a little bit of fear in the kid-- kids.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when I look back at it, I don't care for it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And maybe that's why I treated my own students differently than how I was treated.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But-- and probably, some of them didn't care for-- for Jews, among the faculty.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A Jewish teacher could not get a position in high school.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I know only of one case, only one Jew got a teaching position in elementary school.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But-- oh, in the-- there was a seminar for-- for teachers, a two-year school.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So there, occasionally, would have a Jewish teacher.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But otherwise, nothing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Not in gymnasium.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Not in the high school.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So-- and we took a lot of courses.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But it was different.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We did not take chemistry every day.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We take chemistry three days and physics two days a week.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So we could squeeze in more subjects.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So we took about 10, 11 subjects a year.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And-- but it was a very traditional learning.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But I guess that all over the world at that time, people didn't have this kind of approach to education as now.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I belonged to the Betar.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But this was only over the weekend, because during the week, we really had to work on our homework.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was a lot of homework, and there was no playing around during the week.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "All the activities were taking place during the weekend.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was-- you had all kinds of speakers who came and talked to us.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And as I told you, Jabotinsky was in our house, and so was Begin.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they-- and they enjoyed coming to Ostrog because there was a lot of Zionists there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And most, even the older people, belonged to Zionist organization because they were really persecuted in Russia.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
